content: Great app, would not pick any other than this one. The actually coding for the app could probably be improved but that's me knit-picking.
The app has great information, but the search tool doesn't work at all. Fix that and it would be a 5 Star App
Excellent app with some new knots I've never seen and I have quite a few books. Keep up the good work!
Awesome info in this app, would be 5 stars if the in-app video player was better and the search bar wasn't utterly useless.

program was working good until it started updating itself, now it is not working. 07/02/2019. I did uninstall and reinstall couple times still didn't work. I went to devoloper site checked if it's working, then go back to my installed NetKnots application and checked it and it is working now.
Has every knot that I use and some I want to test

Great app, great interface! No more searching Google for knots while 
working on a project. Good work John, simplicity is king!

Awesome, simple but great. A good selection of all the knots you'll ever need including all the well known ones. Clear illustrations. Fantastic animations that make it so you just can't go wrong. And a favourites list to top it off so your old faithfuls are always there at your fingertips. Thanks.
Great pocket reference for anyone tying down a load to keeping that hog on the end of your fishing line.
What a fabulous and helpful app!  The "how to tie a knot" instructions are really easy to follow.  This will definitely come in handy.  Thanks!

Not knots is my one stop for  anything I do with rope. But they left out the list of alternative knots at the bottom of each knot's page.  They have this on their website. The missing lists of any knot's alternatives  makes finding knots in this app a frustrating, futile exercise.
replyContent: Really, 2 stars? Seems a bit harsh for all this app has going for it. Also, to find an alternative knot just select the category for what you are trying to do: make a Loop, tie a rope to an object, etc, and there you have a list of alternatives. Really not so hard and certainly not a futile exercise.
